Sat Apr 3 2004 Linas Vepstas <linas@linas.org>
	* Prep for 2.1.8 release: tag gnotime-2-1-8
	* ghtml.c, main.c: port from deprecated guile gh_* interface to 
	  new shiny scm_* interface.
